definition.value: Subdivision of thorax, which is the posterior part of the thorax and is demarcated from the chest by the external surface of the posterolateral part of the rib cage and the anterior surface of the thoracic vertebral column; together with the chest, it constitutes the thorax. Examples: There is only one chest.

label.value: Cortex of lobe of cerebral hemisphere

definition.value: Subdivision of neck, which is demarcated from the back of the neck by the plane of the anterior part of the prevertebral fascia; together with the back of the neck, it constitutes the neck. Examples: There is only one front of neck.
